{"tid":362819,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"索羅斯 Q2 2017 部署 18億美元認沽權","createTime":"2017-08-17T08:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T09:00:43.000Z","uid":82382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"372b8b3d515533c898e5c2860297a116a3e48413","tid":362819,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】「金融大鱷」索羅斯今年初曾預言，美國總統特朗普施政的不確定性，將會令市場下挫。根據其家族基金Soros Fund Management向美國證交會（SEC）提交的文件，索羅斯上季似乎繼續押注美股下挫，截至6月30日，其家族基金持有近18億美元的美國規模最大的科技股交易所買賣基金PowerShares QQQ Trust、SPDR標普500指數ETF和安碩羅素2000中小型指數ETF的認沽期權。當中價值逾10億美元的PowerShares QQQ Trust認沽權是上季才買入，規模相當於其投資組合的18%，當指數下滑就可獲利，但次季PowerShares QQQ Trust卻上升。<br />\n<br />\n不過索羅斯也有對冲淡倉的風險，上季也買入了價值4981萬美元的SPDR標普500指數ETF認購期權，並把安碩羅素2000中小型指數ETF的認沽期權，減持了24%。對於強勢科技股，索羅斯的取向各異，上季減持了facebook、微軟，並沽清Alphabet的A股及Netflix，但新買入了7500股亞馬遜。此外，他又大舉增持阿里巴巴的美國存託憑證，按季持倉大幅增加近八成，增持了8.5萬股。他又另建了前身為雅虎的Altaba持倉，價值相當於其投資組合的2.5%。<br />\n<br />\n年初預言特朗普施政 美股會跌<br />\n值得留意的是，大部分基金在首季買入社交媒體Snapchat母公司Snap的股票後，隨即在次季沽清。Moore Capital、Jana Partners、對冲基金大佬David Tepper旗下的Appaloosa都沽清了持倉，只有索羅斯成了Snap的主要投資者。<br />\n索羅斯雖然上季減持了10萬股，但仍持有155萬股，截至6月底這些股份價值為2750萬美元。如今Snap已跌穿17美元招股價，在13美元以下徘徊，索羅斯這筆股票持倉只值1950萬美元左右。<br />\n<br />\n此外，索羅斯增持了一些消費股，包括卡夫亨氏、家樂氏及辦公用品連鎖店Staples，另沽清Tesla、高盛、輝瑞及石油股ConocoPhillips的持倉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2017/8/16/106657-15028802253262746_origin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.seekingalpha.com%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F8%2F16%2F106657-15028802253262746_origin.jpg&h=58df57f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170816/s00004/1502819507156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170816%2Fs00004%2F1502819507156&d=ihz1EdSmBbkfL291Z%2BBk%2FFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=9189fe60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170816%2Fs00004%2F1502819507156&h=c4170337\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170816/s00004/1502819507156</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4099340-tracking-george-soross-portfolio-q2-2017-update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fseekingalpha.com%2Farticle%2F4099340-tracking-george-soross-portfolio-q2-2017-update&d=ihz1EdSmBbkfL291Z%2BBk%2FFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c0a1017d\" target=\"_blank\">https://seekingalpha.com/article/4099340-tracking-george-soross-portfolio-q2-2017-update</a>"},{"pid":"224655ca2b83f6d7c33b06370e81bb78416df2af","tid":362819,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Fat Fat 了"},{"pid":"dd2ac5704a58c9006c465bb77f25442fae882cef","tid":362819,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"又出口術  btw佢死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549933b8ed6b5b05383cb9fb2eacbe77ece0810c","tid":362819,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又出口術  btw佢死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個Portfolio有30%係US大市Put Option<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820d274035d0e9d20a283baf2bf9048c65b357a9","tid":362819,"uid":137180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c27d6dfda6b903fe7a1e942b6d8afa7341b20b9","tid":362819,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T14:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又出口術  btw佢死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 